title: #95 - Man Wants To Legally Change Age & Black Friday Deals No One Wants
description: On this episode of The H3 Podcast Ethan and Hila talk crappy Black Friday deals, Walmart riots, missionaries getting bow and arrowed by native tribes, a man who wants to legally lower his age by 20 years, Ethan's terrible hair, and 95 year old Nazi's getting deported!
